original_title: Tie-Died: Rock 'n Roll's Most Deadicated Fans
overview: Filmed during the Grateful Dead's 1994 summer tour, this film chronicles the lives of the "Deadheads"-- free-spirited fans who follow the band around the country.
tagline: It's more than just the music--it's a way of life!
title: Tie-Died: Rock 'n Roll's Most Deadicated Fans
